        Explainer

&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;tt&gt;Nested pseudo elements styling allows to style ::before::marker and 
&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;::after::marker pseudo elements and will be essential to style 
&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;::column::scroll-marker pseudo elements for the carousel project 
