&gt; Measurement
&gt;
&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://chromestatus.com/metrics/feature/timeline/popularity/4955"&gt;https://chromestatus.com/metrics/feature/timeline/popularity/4955&lt;/a&gt; In
&gt; addition, we have several UMA metrics.
