&gt;&gt; Explainer
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; Use case we want to support:
&gt;&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/w3c-fedid/FedCM/issues/477"&gt;https://github.com/w3c-fedid/FedCM/issues/477&lt;/a&gt;
&gt;&gt;
