&gt;&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/w3c-fedid/FedCM/pull/669"&gt;https://github.com/w3c-fedid/FedCM/pull/669&lt;/a&gt; (account labels)
&gt;&gt;
&gt;
&gt; Most of these are still open, is something blocking finishing and landing
&gt; these spec PRs?
