&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; &gt; (&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/w3ctag/design-reviews/issues/170"&gt;https://github.com/w3ctag/design-reviews/issues/170&lt;/a&gt;, 
