&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; This Intent implies that something else is going on, maybe multiple
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; things.
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; 1. &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/WICG/trust-token-api/issues/106"&gt;https://github.com/WICG/trust-token-api/issues/106&lt;/a&gt; says that
